Black Sabbath - The Last Sacrament(Live Osaka) 1980 ak192

Recorded Live at Festival Hall, Osaka, Japan - November 21, 1980.
Excellent+ Audience Recording -> Bootleg Silver CDs :: CBR `192 kbps
This one is almost impossible to note that is an audience recording, honestly a marvelous one, it sounds more like a radio broadcast, pure quality with the band in top form and long set list

LINEUP: Ronnie James Dio - vocals :: Tony Iommi - guitar :: Geezer Butler - bass guitar :: Vinny Appice - drums
